data.description: The perfect home for those seeking comfort and convenience. This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom house will be available for viewing starting January 1st! Step inside and discover a well-designed layout that offers plenty of room for everyone. The electric appliances in the kitchen make cooking a breeze, while the 2-car garage provides ample space for parking and storage. With washer/dryer connections, laundry day will be a breeze. Stay cozy during the colder months with central heat/air, and enjoy the warmth and ambiance of a fireplace in the living area. The fenced yard offers privacy and security, perfect for outdoor activities or simply enjoying the fresh air. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is close to schools, shopping centers, and entertainment options. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
